Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.15,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:05.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we couldn't sleep, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:18.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about today's "Scare Minorin, Enter the White Knight" plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:23.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,While we're already scared, will we be able to scare Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:25.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do it, the future won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:36.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Something Minorin will be scared of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.84,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "something Minorin will be scared of"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:40.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early! Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:46.15,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of foul plans are you plotting so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Foul plans, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.65,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.54,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,the culprits of what Kushieda was fretting over yesterday were you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.32,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.61,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.79,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:01.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.25,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:08.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Minorin is extremely fond of horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:13.33,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She said she loves being surprised and getting scared, so I wanted to make some summer memories—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.65,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:23.61,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why instead of her being scared, her eyes were glowing with avarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:26.06,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Make me your accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:26.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:26.79,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:28.30,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we work together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:31.27,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,and make Kushieda genuinely frightened!{he uses genuinely here rather.. weirdly.} {est: really, fully,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, look—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.59,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I'll invite Ami too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:36.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid chi' too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.53,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,She's bound to be familiar with the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.60,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll strike while the iron is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, but Kawashima won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.62,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.34,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely talk her into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.50,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Worry, do not!{.. he is talking weird here, so yes, yoda time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.11,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What should we do, Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"What", you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:55.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.04,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:03.08,Ep Titles,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(1001.818182,243)}Fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:03.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Even though I was planning to make breakfast, I got beaten to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.99,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:06.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.10,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, lunchboxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:14.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said they're gonna be playing at the sea for the whole day today, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You got up early for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.97,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Chef, this unworthy Kushieda will be of assistance too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.45,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, order me as you please!{you guessed it}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you slice up the onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.05,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, wholeheartedly glad to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Egg sandwiches and tuna sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:37.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Also, soup from the leftovers of the curry... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.70,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at that, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.79,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you just praise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:49.67,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,With the cleaning yesterday too, you're rather skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Both my parents work, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,When my little brother was at home, I had to make lunchboxes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You have a little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:03.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,He's an active high school baseball player, Akechi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.20,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it got in my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:09.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.49,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah! Gotta peel the apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun's really skilled at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's curry was magnificent too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that big of a thing, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:30.14,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I think that diligent side of you is really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the class doesn't know this side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.13,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:38.17,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever becomes Takasu-kun's bride will be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kyusheda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Takyasu-kyun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-About yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.02,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.63,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,tell anyone about that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.42,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't talked with anyone else about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.97,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.13,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I said more than I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.46,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad it was around Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.03,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.45,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You clumsy-dumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.54,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the cute one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't call me cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.20,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,But, Chef, what shall we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.00,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we mix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we mix it with real force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The sunlight's burning today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.86,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi Angel!{http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E3%81%AEKomachi_Angel}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin's so energetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:29.05,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll do it according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's helping out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.96,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! With Ami's guidance, we set up traps in a nearby cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll get nowhere without her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.30,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.39,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.80,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.06,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy for girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima? You there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.53,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gone on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what are you do—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I was admiring myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.04,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, want to look too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.37,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Isn't this rather risqué?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.06,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this cleavage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.72,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.12,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. You already saw me in a bikini at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.42,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But this part comes off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.12,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Put it back on! Put it back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.57,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Then put it back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,How cold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.07,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to be like that, I'm not going to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:45.84,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Why does Takasu-kun want to make Minori-chan enjoy herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.82,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to tell me, I'm not helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.97,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You got five seconds, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.84,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.49,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,four...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.73,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.79,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.47,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.00,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:03.44,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.34,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Not helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.36,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! With impact, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.04,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,With force, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.04,Alternative,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.90,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.63,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's, like, boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:29.13,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not with us, we won't be able to get around in the caves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.96,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I drew you a map, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.98,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yuusaku, but you'll have to do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.83,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,No problems with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.90,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun was the one who chose after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.67,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Takasu. That Ami suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.\NGoing alone would be difficult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.17,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.53,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,If the two of us leave by ourselves, it might look rather suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.70,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.38,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll somehow manage alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.25,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I've come up with three price-worthy ideas for traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.35,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda will most definitely go half-crazy from fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.25,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kushieda! Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.18,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.05,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Man! It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.14,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun sure is a cooking prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kushieda helped me out after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Minorin did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.13,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,That egg sandwich was mixed with force by yours truly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.49,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Lunch while I'm not around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Announcing to girls with a loud voice that you're going to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.56,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.38,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And besides, you were gone for so long. Just what—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.81,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.93,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Speaking of long—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.88,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What's this consultation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.00,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kushieda. You see, actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.60,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:57.12,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the cove there's a really pretty cave, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.16,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Cave, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.35,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's my special place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Special place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.35,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna take a stroll over there later?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Wah! A stroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.60,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.95,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.36,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, so it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.08,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A-min's special stroll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.33,Danger,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz310.376\pos(850.909091,262.5)}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:20.45,Danger,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz310.376\pos(850.909091,262.5)\clip(m 876 308 l 953 306 782 105 735 140)}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:20.54,Danger,{SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz310.376\pos(850.909091,262.5)\clip(m 876 320 l 962 314 782 105 735 140)}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.54,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What an atmosphere, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:23.33,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.88,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try going in then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.12,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, doesn't it feel like something will come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:30.42,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Like an encounter with an unidentified creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.91,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No, if it was a living thing, it'd be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:35.26,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's make sure to capture it alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:39.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Making him our accomplice was really the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That coaxing's cool too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.48,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.87,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Kitamura's Explorers' League!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.94,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to find the two-headed golden cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark! It's narrow! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.45,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's unexpectedly spacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.45,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being unfocused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.00,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't come here for a simple test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:03.99,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.17,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it goes down a level, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.90,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,The first barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.35,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Fried tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura's got the brains, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.98,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,...he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:32.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't speak ill of Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.28,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it getting cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.65,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Because we've come further in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.36,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.93,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I smell ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.54,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Blood... writing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.09,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,"Gyaaa," it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.71,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's an idiot all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't speak ill of Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.03,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wro—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.12,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Takasu-kun! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.90,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:19.20,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the curse of a brokenhearted woman who lost her way inside this cave and died an unnatural death on a trip of grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.09,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.83,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.63,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Nice assist, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.63,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{daseee}{\an8}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.12,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{dachi-}{\an8}Let me leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.21,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You set up some traps too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.41,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{noroi da}{\an8}It's a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.23,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,My final trap is fifty meters up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.33,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{osoroshi}{\an8}It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.60,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:35.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.04,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kushieda! Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun's skilled after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin's really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, not me either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not part of the setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The same as last night... for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.58,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! Three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.26,Alternative,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous alone, let's hold hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.33,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Really! Let's tie up! Let's tie up real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:02.97,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm all warmed up now, so let's go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.45,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.73,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use a shortcut to go back before everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawashima! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.08,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going even further in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.71,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,This is the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:23.72,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.50,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Where're Ami and Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:30.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really know the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.33,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that uneasy about being separated from the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really good with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,dark places and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.68,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.06,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,what would Takasu-kun do if I left you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.12,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.62,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be uneasy from being separated from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.67,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.96,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Would you think that you don't want to be separated from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.76,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.84,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to return to Minori as fast as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:07.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.20,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that girl suits Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— it's not like I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.60,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's suitable for Takasu-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:19.82,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:20.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:22.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.40,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:26.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.15,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't kid about something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.50,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kitamura and the others will come looking for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid! I'm here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.18,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No! You don't need to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.46,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That I was lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.58,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would ever get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.65,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,D-u-m-m-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.77,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.14,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Takasu-kun! I'm getting slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.03,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But! Takasu-kun was acting just like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.42,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.24,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,a very dull guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But that part of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.08,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.93,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier I said Minori-chan wasn't suited for Takasu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.51,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I really meant that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.44,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Takasu-kun's the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Minori-chan's the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.08,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,By being at her side,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.74,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd simply get burned away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:39.19,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Takasu-kun wouldn't hit Minori-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.16,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be equal simply with admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.18,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,The one you can be equal with would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.34,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.47,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That was—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,—Kushieda's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.04,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wai— Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.27,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.36,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu! Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.54,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You were all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, where's Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.41,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.23,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.53,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda was taken by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.84,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.03,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me by that, Kushieda was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.80,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Out of batteries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.80,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, lend me yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.15,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? This sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.66,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,A voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.48,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.84,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kitamu—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.68,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun! Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.18,Alternative,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, don't get separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{toriaezu}For now, stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore. When it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat it to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.39,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh— wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.02,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, an accident has occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.05,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We must rescue Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:07.93,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.19,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:14.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.33,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Akechi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am indeed Kushieda Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.86,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.62,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.63,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,my partner in crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.02,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,The hair in Takasu's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,and the scattered clothes in Taiga's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,those and everything else was all our doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.14,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.14,Alternative,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the way you were trying to scare me was so amateurish, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.89,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up wanting to teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.97,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Showing you that this is how you scare people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:05.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That means... you had exposed us already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,When you two are lurking around like that on your own, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.36,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I made Kitamura-kun my accomplice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.53,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,and started trapping you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.49,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,But I had fun. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.17,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:22.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I really love horror!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.69,Alternative,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.50,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it the "Manjuu Kowai" method.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.89,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,If I say "I'm scared of ghosts," "I'm scared of the occult,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.73,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,someone's bound to try to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.99,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I would gladly receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.44,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And now that we're done telling you the gig...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's lit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.09,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Today really was one hell of a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.87,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Really, that was so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,About the conversation earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really give you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:53.61,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's not about whether I'd be lonely or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about whether you'd be lonely or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.91,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really considered whether I'm lonely or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.05,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets painful, just straightforwardly express that emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.35,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.87,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.36,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,kind sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.81,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.14,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last night. Are you enjoying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.47,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:41.72,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely fooled and utterly frightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,but when I'm with you, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.82,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.79,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I really had fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.81,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And the curry was also really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:06.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And you listened to my strange little tale without laughing at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.58,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun properly understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.77,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.19,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to show Takasu-kun ghosts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up kinda overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.17,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.12,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said you wanted to see ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:24.94,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Takasu-kun want to scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:25.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.84,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:31.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga told me that you were scared of horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to tease me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.50,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.67,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun would never do something to someone that they dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.26,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type who's always considering how to make someone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sono takasukun}Why did that Takasu-kun do something like this, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.31,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.79,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I really think it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make you believe that ghosts exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's too early to give up just because you can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.66,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, next we'll go find a UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.95,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,One that isn't a man-made satellite — a real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:14.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And after a UFO, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.78,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A Tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.86,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,And then, if we keep finding the things I want to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.16,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,if my world has been changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.46,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:26.95,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.48,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,An exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.58,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,UFO is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.54,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I really saw one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I saw one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden outbreak of a galactic war, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth will be protected by us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.95,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,The trip continues till you're home, you know!
